[normal]of 
[normal]staff and management of the UK Emergency service
[normal]s of 
[normal]Train Operating Company, British Transport Police, and NHS staff in rendering assistance to the affected members of public 
[normal]in the aftermath of accident 
[normal]are good and are not studied in this paper
[normal] (Regulator, 2008)
[normal]. 
