[normal]Near miss events are warning signs of impending disasters. 
[normal]Humanity has had to deal with false alarms as well as real alarms disguised as noisy signals in relat
[normal]ion to the impending danger. Decision theorists have spent their efforts to explain illusion of validity of our skills and knowledge learnt in one environment to their application in other environment. The concept of illusion of validity is discussed by No
